name: Gabriella Chaggas
description:
Gabriella Chaggas

Instagram Model

She's got fewer than 50k followers, but I don't give a fuck because she's hotter than the sun.

Based on 1.4 and a learning rate of 5e-03, I ran it only 5000 steps and chose the 2500 step version to present here.

Unlike the Cecelia Lion embedding I made a few weeks ago, Gabriella's magnificent hair seems to gen perfectly. No idea why.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
